 ('20', '25', 'en_us', 'About Me', '<p>Ever since I could hold a crayon, I’ve scribbled, colored, and made things. Today, I scribble and color less, and illustrate, design, and code more.</p>', NULL, 'About me: Who IS Joseph Wilson?', '', '<p>I like things that look good and work well, and I love to work and play by creating. If you’re in need of a developer, designer, illustrator, or some combination of the three, email me, and let’s talk. I’d love to hear from you!</p>', '<p>Ever since I could hold a crayon, I’ve scribbled, colored, and made things. Today, I scribble and color less, and illustrate, design, and code more.</p>', NULL, '2017-05-11 01:18:19', '2017-05-11 18:34:29', '2ffe3dcf-165e-4d5c-bb65-2707d3edf7d1'),
 ('21', '26', 'en_us', 'About Me Header', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-05-11 01:20:34', '2017-05-11 01:20:34', '94befb5e-6fdb-486f-8eb6-58d74f46c4d8'),
