 ('23', '34', 'en_us', 'Web Development', NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, '<p>It started 16 years ago with a behemoth of a book<sup><a href=\"http://craft.jgwilsondesign.dev/admin/entries/webDevelopmentIndex/34-web-development-index#footnotes-1\"></a><a href=\"#footnotes-1\"></a><a href=\"#footnotes-1\"></a><a href=\"#footnotes-1\">1</a></sup> my dad purchased on building websites with HTML. Now I build more than just websites. I build <em>experiences</em>.</p>', NULL, '2017-05-11 18:23:09', '2017-05-15 22:14:35', '2f3cda75-edf1-4efc-af05-7eaf4aa9e015'),
 ('24', '41', 'en_us', 'Illustration', NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, '<p>As an artist, I’m mostly inspired by classic Disney animation and comic book art. But I love so many styles and enjoy the challenge of meeting my client’s needs, no matter the style!</p>', NULL, '2017-05-11 20:41:16', '2017-05-16 21:34:57', '076e22ed-4f24-4bb1-babe-580593242e80'),
