 ('30', '34', '9', '1', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Web Development\",\"slug\":\"web-development-index\",\"postDate\":1494526989,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"28\":\"\",\"40\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"footnote\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"footnoteId\":\"1\",\"footnoteText\":\"<p>[1]&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/Teach-Yourself-Publishing-Professional-Reference\\/dp\\/0672322048\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Sams Teach Yourself Web Publishing With HTML and XHTML in 21 Days, Professional Reference Edition<\\/a><\\/p>\"}}},\"44\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"heading\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"More Web Development Work\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"images\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":\"\"}}},\"25\":\"\",\"26\":\"\",\"24\":\"\",\"43\":\"<p>It started 16 years ago with a behemoth of a book<sup><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/craft.jgwilsondesign.dev\\/admin\\/entries\\/webDevelopmentIndex\\/34-web-development-index#footnotes-1\\\"><\\/a><a href=\\\"#footnotes-1\\\">1<\\/a><\\/sup>&nbsp;my dad purchased on building websites with HTML. Now I build more than just websites. I build&nbsp;<em>experiences<\\/em>.<\\/p>\",\"51\":\"\"}}', '2017-05-11 18:34:06', '2017-05-11 18:34:06', '02922a17-77c5-4f15-b0df-d376a0767cf3'),
 ('31', '25', '7', '1', 'en_us', '5', '', '{\"typeId\":\"7\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"About Me\",\"slug\":\"about\",\"postDate\":1494465986,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"27\":\"<p>I like things that look good and work well, and I love to work and play by creating. If you\\u2019re in need of a developer, designer, illustrator, or some combination of the three, email me, and let\\u2019s talk. I\\u2019d love to hear from you!<\\/p>\",\"3\":{\"28\":{\"type\":\"trivia\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"triviaHeading\":\"Learner of Things\",\"triviaBody\":\"<p>I\\u2019m almost entirely self-taught in everything I do. Almost. (That means I\\u2019ve consumed a lot of video tutorials on YouTube and articles all across the web.) I have always loved to learn new things and am a self-starter.<\\/p>\",\"triviaImage\":\"\"}},\"29\":{\"type\":\"trivia\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"triviaHeading\":\"Lover of Animation\",\"triviaBody\":\"<p>At the age of 13, I made the decision that I would be a character animator when I grew up. Even though I might not be an animator yet, I figure I\\u2019m still growing up&hellip; So there\\u2019s still a chance.<\\/p>\",\"triviaImage\":\"\"}},\"30\":{\"type\":\"trivia\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"triviaHeading\":\"Reader of Books\",\"triviaBody\":\"<p>I don\\u2019t read as much as I\\u2019d like, but I do seem to collect books so there\\u2019s always something to pick from. My favorite just-for-fun read is still&nbsp;<em>Ender\\u2019s Game<\\/em>, by Orson Scott Card.<\\/p>\",\"triviaImage\":\"\"}},\"31\":{\"type\":\"trivia\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"triviaHeading\":\"Watcher of Great Films\",\"triviaBody\":\"<p>At last count, I own&nbsp;<strong>351<\\/strong>&nbsp;movies. And I\\u2019ve seen far more than that. I love movies. I love the way they combine so many artistic disciplines into one final product. (Bonus fact: I\\u2019ve noticed that I tend to buy more movies when I don\\u2019t have Netflix.)<\\/p>\",\"triviaImage\":\"\"}},\"32\":{\"type\":\"trivia\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"triviaHeading\":\"Traveler of Places\",\"triviaBody\":\"<p>When I was a kid, my dad was in the US Air Force. That means I had the huge privilege of getting to travel the country. I haven\\u2019t done any traveling outside the US, though, except when I was born in Germany while my parents were stationed there.<\\/p>\",\"triviaImage\":[\"27\"]}}},\"28\":{\"33\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"<p>I\\u2019ve always had an eye for design and detail, and that\\u2019s a huge part of what makes me the successful developer and designer that I am today. Surprisingly, it all happened by accident. An entire decade ago, I wanted a website to bring people together to help me work on an animation project I was doing while in high school, so I built it. The animation never really got anywhere, but I learned enough about web development to land my first job. Since that day 10 years ago, I\\u2019ve been using, refining, and growing those skills, continuing to learn and keep pace with the rapidly-changing web and its technologies.<\\/p>\",\"newSection\":\"newSection\"}}},\"21\":[\"26\"],\"25\":\"\",\"26\":\"\",\"24\":\"About me: Who IS Joseph Wilson?\",\"43\":\"<p>Ever since I could hold a crayon, I\\u2019ve scribbled, colored, and made things. Today, I scribble and color less, and illustrate, design, and code more.<\\/p>\"}}', '2017-05-11 18:34:29', '2017-05-11 18:34:29', '416c8d15-5cff-4b7c-9b35-9ce708837cf4'),
 ('32', '2', '1', '1', 'en_us', '5', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"I\\u2019m Wilson.\",\"slug\":\"homepage\",\"postDate\":1492722062,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"28\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"<p>I\\u2019ve been a professional web designer and front end developer for ten years. And illustration and the art of making things look good have been a passion of mine my entire life!<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Here are a few of the tools I use to get the job done:<\\/p>\",\"newSection\":\"newSection\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"iconList\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"icon\":\"\",\"isNewSection\":\"newSection\"}},\"new3\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"<p>Check out the&nbsp;<a href=\\\"\\/about\\\">About<\\/a>&nbsp;page to learn more.<\\/p>\",\"newSection\":\"newSection\"}}},\"25\":\"\",\"26\":\"\",\"24\":\"\",\"43\":\"<p>I\\u2019m a passionate creative based in Portland, Oregon. I&nbsp;<a href=\\\"\\/web\\\">build great experiences for the web<\\/a>&nbsp;and I&nbsp;<a href=\\\"\\/art\\\">draw all kinds of things<\\/a>, too!<\\/p>\"}}', '2017-05-11 18:38:34', '2017-05-11 18:38:34', '2f918db8-a2bb-419e-b201-d52dc0258082'),
