ng and that meant illustrations!<\\/p>\",\"newSection\":\"none\"}},\"new1\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"72\",\"73\",\"71\"],\"layout\":\"wide\",\"isNewSection\":\"none\"}},\"65\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"<p>But not all illustrations are created equal. The final illustration I completed was a large banner that they wanted to use as the first thing people saw when visiting the site. This single piece was really the culmination of everything I had done leading up to it. So I started it off with a teeny tiny thumbnail based on the direction I had received. (Fortunately for me, Jean-Marc, the co-founder and president of the company, was fantastic at giving direction. He knew what he wanted and gave me just enough freedom to make this one of my favorite projects of all time. So far.)<\\/p>\",\"newSection\":\"none\"}},\"66\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"<p>From there it was on to the illustration.<\\/p>\",\"newSection\":\"none\"}},\"58\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"57\"],\"layout\":\"block\",\"isNewSection\":\"none\"}},\"67\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"<p>The process was grueling. The tassels and carrots took what seemed an eternity to finish. And while the pencil stage is my favorite, I will never forget how sore my hand was from the endless hours of thoughtfully placing each line.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>But the results were worth every effort.<\\/p>\",\"newSection\":\"none\"}},\"68\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"59\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"isNewSection\":\"none\"}},\"69\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"60\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"isNewSection\":\"none\"}},\"70\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"<p>It took several weeks to create this one piece, from start to finish. Good thing I did it digitally or else I would have been waiting for paint to dry and who knows how long that would have taken! All in all, this was an amazing project and I feel so privileged and blessed to have worked with such awesome people.<\\/p>\",\"newSection\":\"none\"}},\"56\":{\"type\":\"testimonial\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"testimony\":[\"7\"],\"isNewSection\":\"none\"}}},\"54\":[\"51\"],\"53\":\"IndieRabbit\",\"21\":[\"49\"],\"55\":\"<p><em>IndieRabbit<\\/em>&nbsp;was a small web startup that offered a unique distribution platform for independent filmmakers and their audience members. It was my task to design a mascot for the company as well as to produce several illustrations for their marketing materials and site.<\\/p>\",\"20\":[\"50\"],\"56\":[\"characterDesign\",\"illustration\"],\"25\":\"\",\"26\":\"\",\"24\":\"\"}}', '2017-05-11 23:57:27', '2017-05-11 23:57:27', 'be2d0cb3-1edc-43e2-933b-2ab24052dac1'),
