INSERT INTO `craft_matrixcontent_abouttrivia` (`id`, `elementId`, `locale`, `field_trivia_triviaHeading`, `field_trivia_triviaBody`, `dateCreated`, `dateUpdated`, `uid`) VALUES
 ('1', '28', 'en_us', 'Learner of Things', '<p>I’m almost entirely self-taught in everything I do. Almost. (That means I’ve consumed a lot of video tutorials on YouTube and articles all across the web.) I have always loved to learn new things and am a self-starter.</p>', '2017-05-11 01:25:31', '2017-05-11 18:34:29', '96e438c9-328b-45de-98dd-110233b265e2'),
 ('2', '29', 'en_us', 'Lover of Animation', '<p>At the age of 13, I made the decision that I would be a character animator when I grew up. Even though I might not be an animator yet, I figure I’m still growing up… So there’s still a chance.</p>', '2017-05-11 01:25:31', '2017-05-11 18:34:29', 'b4e2a5ce-07ab-46e9-ad1a-35d7a4bfe483'),
 ('3', '30', 'en_us', 'Reader of Books', '<p>I don’t read as much as I’d like, but I do seem to collect books so there’s always something to pick from. My favorite just-for-fun read is still <em>Ender’s Game</em>, by Orson Scott Card.</p>', '2017-05-11 01:25:31', '2017-05-11 18:34:29', '6dcfb8f7-9a05-44d1-8485-ca87e6b7c38d'),
 ('4', '31', 'en_us', 'Watcher of Great Films', '<p>At last count, I own <strong>351</strong> movies. And I’ve seen far more than that. I love movies. I love the way they combine so many artistic disciplines into one final product. (Bonus fact: I’ve noticed that I tend to buy more movies when I don’t have Netflix.)</p>', '2017-05-11 01:25:31', '2017-05-11 18:34:29', 'd087f8a3-119a-49e1-aa67-b364929d0d34'),
 ('5', '32', 'en_us', 'Traveler of Places', '<p>When I was a kid, my dad was in the US Air Force. That means I had the huge privilege of getting to travel the country. I haven’t done any traveling outside the US, though, except when I was born in Germany while my parents were stationed there.</p>', '2017-05-11 01:25:31', '2017-05-11 18:34:29', '879a8959-35f4-4459-8969-e5a1f62f0b07');
INSERT INTO `craft_matrixcontent_articlebody` (`id`, `elementId`, `locale`, `field_text_text`, `field_text_isNewSection`, `field_quote_quote`, `field_quote_cite`, `field_quote_company`, `field_quote_role`, `field_quote_isNewSection`, `field_image_layout`, `field_image_isNewSection`, `field_iconList_isNewSection`, `field_testimonial_isNewSection`, `dateCreated`, `dateUpdated`, `uid`) VALUES
 ('1', '33', 'en_us', '<p>I’ve always had an eye for design and detail, and that’s a huge part of what makes me the successful developer and designer that I am today. Surprisingly, it all happened by accident. An entire decade ago, I wanted a website to bring people together to help me work on an animation project I was doing while in high school, so I built it. The animation never really got anywhere, but I learned enough about web development to land my first job. Since that day 10 years ago, I’ve been using, refining, and growing those skills, continuing to learn and keep pace with the rapidly-changing web and its technologies.</p>', 'newSection', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-05-11 04:53:23', '2017-05-11 18:34:29', '45bf3e2c-4329-4b29-b63d-c4f819543910'),
 ('2', '38', 'en_us', '<p>I’ve been a professional web designer and front end developer for ten years. And illustration and the art of making things look good have been a passion of mine my entire life!</p>\n<p>Here are a few of the tools I use to get the job done:</p>', 'newSection', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-05-11 18:38:34', '2017-05-13 03:53:26', 'fa298b22-b949-4372-89aa-b70f63413088'),
 ('3', '39', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', NULL, '2017-05-11 18:38:34', '2017-05-13 03:53:26', 'b1ad398f-93cd-4e28-85cf-6cc854740643'),
 ('4', '40', 'en_us', '<p>Check out the <a href=\"/about\">About</a> page to learn more.</p>', 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-05-11 18:38:34', '2017-05-13 03:53:26', '25834390-bf2d-4598-94e6-a08e46797ed7'),
 ('7', '45', 'en_us', '<p>Aside from the occasional use of pencil and paper, I’m a full-fledged digital artist, producing the bulk of my work on the computer using these programs and tools:</p>', 'newSection', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-05-11 20:45:57', '2017-05-16 21:34:57', '8726778d-7de0-435d-9cdc-f7354b4dc564'),
 ('8', '46', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', NULL, '2017-05-11 20:45:57', '2017-05-16 21:34:57', '6db0a0bc-c24c-4bee-afe2-7af8148af0f4'),
 ('9', '55', 'en_us', '<h2>Character Design</h2>\n<p>There is <em>always</em> more to it than what’s directly on the surface. When designing this character, for example, it’s not just a matter of drawing a rabbit. You have to understand the personality of the character you’re trying to create. And in the case of a mascot, that personality becomes or represents the personality of the whole company.</p>\n<p>Right at the start of the project, the team at <em>IndieRabbit</em> wanted a character that was a “…classy, cool, and relatable rabbit that is a bit human…in a classic/graphic cartoon style.”</p>', 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-05-11 20:58:06', '2017-05-16 22:35:05', 'b0bc2b1a-002b-4c5d-b09b-e0f99e29d37e'),
 ('10', '56', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', '2017-05-11 21:11:33', '2017-05-16 22:35:05', '01a663f3-6d79-4564-897b-118e878b4135'),
 ('11', '58', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'block', 'none', NULL, NULL, '2017-05-11 23:20:27', '2017-05-16 22:35:05', '7b538f35-a9e7-404b-bd96-a7dd865a5940'),
 ('12', '61', 'en_us', '<p>Even with all of the concept sketches I did, I still hadn’t quite figured out the character (who we officially named Indy Rabbit). It wasn’t until I started experimenting with facial expressions and refining from there that I really got a feel for “who he is”.</p>', 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-05-11 23:52:43', '2017-05-16 22:35:05', '36bb13d2-926b-44af-a4f2-a741ec156e06'),
 ('13', '62', 'en_us', '<p>Once I had the face, it’s like the body naturally drew itself from there. After a few minor tweaks, it was time to start creating some costumes…</p>', 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-05-11 23:52:43', '2017-05-16 22:35:05', 'bfa60884-d8ad-4d37-8d33-f4ca6fd52faf'),
 ('14', '63', 'en_us', '<p>…before landing on a living, breathing character with life and personality!</p>', 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-05-11 23:52:43', '2017-05-16 22:35:05', '37b116c0-fc7b-4abf-83d1-6c4bde6aeeaa'),
 ('15', '64', 'en_us', '<h2>Website Illustrations</h2>\n<p>Obviously, the goal in designing Indy was to use him in marketing and that meant illustrations!</p>', 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-05-11 23:52:43', '2017-05-16 22:35:05', '463d8885-db8b-423f-9248-e214b4b5af3b'),
 ('16', '65', 'en_us', '<p>But not all illustrations are created equal. The final illustration I completed was a large banner that they wanted to use as the first thing people saw when visiting the site. This single piece was really the culmination of everything I had done leading up to it. So I started it off with a teeny tiny thumbnail based on the direction I had received. (Fortunately for me, Jean-Marc, the co-founder and president of the company, was fantastic at giving direction. He knew what he wanted and gave me just enough freedom to make this one of my favorite projects of all time. So far.)</p>', 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-05-11 23:52:43', '2017-05-16 22:35:05', 'a4086d7d-e8d1-4ed5-9af7-2a3d04ecc2c1'),
 ('17', '66', 'en_us', '<p>From there it was on to the illustration.</p>', 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-05-11 23:52:43', '2017-05-16 22:35:05', '9eb7def7-b0c6-4e62-bab6-2e0b2d3ef89d'),
 ('18', '67', 'en_us', '<p>The process was grueling. The tassels and carrots took what seemed an eternity to finish. And while the pencil stage is my favorite, I will never forget how sore my hand was from the endless hours of thoughtfully placing each line.</p>\n<p>But the results were worth every effort.</p>', 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-05-11 23:52:43', '2017-05-16 22:35:05', '9c13170c-9c3c-4a04-8516-290aafb1b059'),
 ('19', '68', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'full', 'none', NULL, NULL, '2017-05-11 23:52:43', '2017-05-16 22:35:05', '34c4e0c6-639a-469e-b27c-69abb1452b92'),
 ('20', '69', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'full', 'none', NULL, NULL, '2017-05-11 23:52:43', '2017-05-16 22:35:05', '0ae56ab5-040e-4882-993c-9462c842f776'),
 ('21', '70', 'en_us', '<p>It took several weeks to create this one piece, from start to finish. Good thing I did it digitally or else I would have been waiting for paint to dry and who knows how long that would have taken! All in all, this was an amazing project and I feel so privileged and blessed to have worked with such awesome people.</p>', 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-05-11 23:52:43', '2017-05-16 22:35:05', '6d1c9655-06ff-48b3-97e0-55d92e3fbd22'),
 ('22', '74', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'wide', 'none', NULL, NULL, '2017-05-11 23:57:27', '2017-05-16 22:35:05', '0d53b72a-d2b3-44a9-8175-a9f0916f8423'),
 ('23', '76', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'block', 'none', NULL, NULL, '2017-05-12 00:01:25', '2017-05-16 22:35:05', '095e25ff-194a-4c60-8d03-f5386e761ba8'),
 ('24', '78', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'block', 'none', NULL, NULL, '2017-05-12 00:07:18', '2017-05-16 22:35:05', 'aa3a280d-7ecc-427d-8622-b3a7055838c3'),
 ('25', '114', 'en_us', '<p>While I always love the challenge of learning new technologies, here are the tools that I use most to develop my web projects:</p>', 'newSection', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-05-15 21:46:47', '2017-05-15 22:14:35', '80c85ef7-090d-4056-8057-224f39b6b4bf'),
